20
00:02:09.000 --> 00:02:16.000
Elliott Hedman: I didn't code any of them, and I didn't do any graphic design. That's the magic of Cursor or Claude Code. Cursor's the same kind of thing as Claude Code.

21
00:02:17.000 --> 00:02:24.000
Elliott Hedman: Cursor can use Gemini, which does a better job with the visual stuff. You'll probably want to learn both at some point, but we might as well start with the one that's a little better on visual stuff. It's a little easier to use, I think.

22
